sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FTS as Full-Text Search
    participant Cache as Redis

    Client->>Endpoint: GET /api/v1/shared-games?q=azul&minPlayers=2

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract query params
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create SearchSharedGamesQuery

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(query)

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(query)

    Handler->>Cache: TryGetCached("search:azul:minPlayers=2")
    Cache-->>Handler: Cache miss

    Handler->>FTS: Build FTS query
    Note over FTS: to_tsvector('italian', Title || Description)

    Handler->>DB: Execute search query
    Note over DB: WHERE to_tsvector(...) @@ to_tsquery('azul')<br/>AND MinPlayers >= 2<br/>AND Status = Published<br/>AND NOT IsDeleted<br/>ORDER BY ts_rank DESC

    DB-->>Handler: List<SharedGame>

    Handler->>Handler: Apply additional filters
    Note over Handler: Categories, mechanics, player count

    Handler->>Handler: Map to SharedGameDto[]

    Handler->>DB: Count total results
    DB-->>Handler: TotalCount = 5

    Handler->>Cache: SetCached("search:azul:minPlayers=2", result, TTL: 5min)
    Cache-->>Handler: Cached ✓

    Handler-->>Mediator: PaginatedSearchResult
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: PaginatedSearchResult

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {games[], pagination: {totalCount: 5}}
